# =============================================================================
# UTAH ICAC – DOMINIC LYNN CHRISTENSEN PRESS RELEASE EXAMPLE
# =============================================================================
#
# ARTICLE MAPPING SUMMARY
# - Offender:
#   - "Dominic Lynn Christensen, 24" -> ex:11f53d30-a75c-500d-b7d4-f73aab63d796 (uco-identity:Person,
#     cacontology-registry:RegisteredSexOffender, cacontology-registry:RecidivistSexOffender).
# - Prior 2021 cases (Sanpete County):
#   - May 2021 forcible sexual abuse while 18-year-old victim sleeps -> ex:be8f34fd-923e-55b8-a72a-fae96c23a323
#     (cacontology:ChildSexualAbuseEvent) located in ex:ccec1c1c-defa-5945-aff1-c8c5c864ffcd and linked to
#     ex:e4e70488-8886-5573-95bd-0885a5689ede (18-year-old) and ex:11f53d30-a75c-500d-b7d4-f73aab63d796.
#   - July 2021 online/offline relationship with 15-year-old and photos with 11-year-old ->
#     ex:da1c6db2-8d82-5de5-a8db-f22b0743f98d (cacontology:ChildSexualAbuseEvent) and ex:ca6b84f0-65ff-5784-9a03-b8cc66840047
#     (cacontology:CSAMIncident) with multiple juvenile victims.
#   - "playing a game with sexual consequences with several juveniles" -> modeled as
#     ex:17a9eaac-1a26-5aa8-960a-42ffa1184606 (cacontology-grooming:PhysicalSpaceGrooming) to reuse
#     existing grooming patterns for offline, multi-victim sexualized games.
#   - Charges "forcible sexual abuse", "sexual exploitation of a minor", "sexual abuse of a child"
#     -> ex:830477dc-1655-56a1-802e-cb40903d732c, ex:9e450cae-582b-5993-982f-fb8babf24d14,
#        ex:1dfe3c61-2953-5be1-b5c6-f2ffa5caf291 (cacontology-legal-outcomes:StateCharge) with
#        sentencing resources ex:0550f100-c17d-56b4-8097-d2ae9820bd24 and ex:561c8464-0aa3-5997-bbaa-9451c977d192
#        capturing 364 days jail and 48 months probation served concurrently.
# - Registry status & compliance:
#   - Article text that he is a "sex offender" and later "facing charges for failure to register or
#     providing false info as a sex offender" -> ex:0ffa5181-0574-5a79-94ef-d5d9ec1b0b32
#     (cacontology-registry:RegistrationRecord) and ex:fcde8bdb-2675-5262-9e52-7daf75ace220
#     (cacontology-registry:ComplianceViolation) linked to ex:11f53d30-a75c-500d-b7d4-f73aab63d796.
# - Current 2025 NCMEC-driven case (Garfield County):
#   - August 21 cybertip where "NCMEC received a tip that a specific user had uploaded child sexual
#     abuse material" -> ex:144f3e6a-91ca-5b19-891e-72faf487d978 (cacontology-us-ncmec:NCMECCybertipReport) with
#     ex:1851988e-d905-52a1-9a2a-2bc65fb1248b (cacontology-us-ncmec:OnlineEnticementIncident) and
#     ex:7d5275ac-a296-5542-b2c2-80f76c3fab7d (cacontology:CSAMIncident).
#   - "email address, username, and IP address" -> ex:c7af5f45-2475-5a1c-bb2a-f48142f190ce
#     (uco-observable:DigitalAccount), ex:4aefcd45-89e1-5148-b984-9e11b7f7c02e (uco-observable:ObservableObject
#     with descriptive value), linked via NCMEC AccountLinking pattern.
#   - "search warrant to the email provider" -> ex:LegalProcess_SearchWarrantEmail
#     (uco-action:Action) with rdfs:comment; investigation modeled as ex:a8fb0031-7ccf-5982-8078-060e6441ca72
#     (cacontology:CACInvestigation).
#   - "contents between Christensen’s account and another user... juvenile female" and "CSAM showing
#     adults sexually assaulting children" -> ex:e9930072-5403-5363-840e-2f8473ffe6a0 (cacontology-grooming:ChildVictim)
#     and ex:db66d7d7-8d35-54c4-8b07-6f00728c5450 (uco-observable:DigitalArtifact) linked to the CSAM incident.
#   - New charges "seven counts of sexual exploitation of a minor" in Garfield County and "failure to
#     register or providing false info as a sex offender" -> ex:Charge_2025_SexualExploitationMinor
#     and ex:2c89067e-1006-5a1c-b17a-0c3cdda4b5f1 (cacontology-legal-outcomes:StateCharge).
#   - "held without bail in Garfield County Jail" and initial appearance set for November 20, 2025 ->
#     captured via rdfs:comment on ex:PretrialDetention_2025 (uco-action:Action) because current
#     sentencing ontology does not yet have explicit bail status modeling.
#
# This example intentionally reuses existing CAC Ontology modules (core, grooming, sentencing,
# sex-offender-registry, US NCMEC) and highlights ontology gaps such as:
# - Lack of explicit failure-to-register / false-information charge classes in registry/sentencing.
# - No dedicated bail / held-without-bail representation.
# - No specialized "sexual consequence game" grooming subtype (approximated with PhysicalSpaceGrooming).

